summary: AN ORDINANCE authorizing execution fo a Memorandum of Understanding amending Appendix "H" of the collective bargaining agreement between The City of Seattle and the Joint Crafts Council and its affiliate, the International Brotherhood of Teamsters, Chauffeurs, Warehousemen and Helpers of America, Local No. 882, to add the titles of Parking Attendant, Senior Parking Attendant and Parking Coordinator.
